flowchart LR
    Facts[Persisted facts\npatient history, selected resource, ETA]
    Engine[Deterministic scheduler\nselects route]
    Prompt[Prompt builder]
    Adapter[Provider-agnostic\nGemini adapter]
    Text[Patient explanation\nor six-section doctor brief]
    Cache[(Source-hash cache)]
    Fallback[Deterministic fallback text]
    UI[Patient and doctor views]

    Engine -->|decision facts only| Facts
    Facts --> Prompt
    Prompt --> Adapter
    Adapter -->|success| Text
    Text --> Cache
    Cache --> UI
    Adapter -->|timeout or unavailable| Fallback
    Fallback --> UI
    UI -. never writes decisions .-> Engine

